iw","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"Probabilístico → Aleatorio","guid":"TSU-3lE06Xjw_-or_0w2lg","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"No probabilístico → No aleatorio","guid":"piTKxcKEJYyePiQo2dGZRA","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"1","text":"Parámetro: Medida que caracteriza la población","guid":"YT5ZXKFJyX2_ada8_cwztA","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"1","text":"Estadístico (Estadígrafo): Medida que caracteriza la muestra","guid":"RftsobXkEEbVdTuUDKIP3w","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"1","text":"Fuentes de datos","guid":"TFnm8LJ_WnEAJ2exzDh9Nw","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"Primarias → Datos creados para responder preguntas específicas (OPS, 2018)","guid":"DD8JmZuUa6gRYT5sTFSeig","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"Secundarias → Datos recopilados con propósitos amplios (ej. Encuesta Nacional de Salud)","guid":"QXsdtMjr8JUlzkPPakd78g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"Wjw0A2rAVtxcuBUNyhHFRA","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"Definición: Estudio de ocurrencia y distribución de salud en poblaciones (Samet et al., 2009)","guid":"qH77WIYWTGn82IQhmzPw0Q","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"19","text":"Tipos de Estudio","guid":"ADUsElAmSEzMmml0NAsqVQ","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"Observacionales → Sin intervención del investigador","guid":"CbluzdzK4u02nHnEj5wskw","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"Descriptivos → Describen variables en un grupo","guid":"cgTJnzVuybmoaFIplzN4tg","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"21","text":"Analíticos → Relacionan comparativamente grupos","guid":"oXh6xRFFwI7aSWxCbj8KKA","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"21","text":"Experimentales → Con intervención, valoran efecto (Manterola & Otzen, 2014)","guid":"Fe7PFH7CoD232wQHgqs2_g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"0","text":"Variables\\NEstadísticas","guid":"JgnzQEOep8BQu9NRzB85tQ","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Variable: Característica observada en diferentes sujetos","guid":"pFufs3BldlN66Lwt5SBZJw","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"Variables y\\NBases de Datos","guid":"rMoKpIJPf8k7EKWnz1fCVQ","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"Datos → Materia prima de la bioestadística","guid":"aykoJYR88hH0tV2o_uDGuA","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"28","text":"Variables → Cualidades/cantidades de cada individuo, son variables (≠ constantes)","guid":"yXPhQpvoluajJTUcfuN4oA","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"28","text":"Tipos de variables → Importante distinguir para evitar errores en análisis y procedimientos estadísticos (1)","guid":"s2UrlTDzMh46cD-giJSCXg","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"26","text":"Tipos de\\NVariables","guid":"XUR5e5X2Kuwn5ofNiSLhqg","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"Cualitativas (Categóricas)","guid":"5JwmF9hdu607zIYrYp42FQ","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"Nominales → No ordenables (p.ej., sexo, estado civil, grupo de tratamiento)","guid":"CIF4ycQRUtwz0YTSy15sUQ","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"Tipos:","guid":"oQ8EEM6nUjknAToGdLiK-Q","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"Dicotómicas (binarias): 2 categorías (p.ej., sano/enfermo)","guid":"2BJXllow1y0IUmGCKw7mGQ","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"35","text":"Policotómicas: Múltiples categorías (p.ej., grupo sanguíneo)","guid":"ApHA3WEZXMLvroFuBjtt6g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"32","text":"Variables\\NCualitativas Ordinales","guid":"uxJsO361by0jppjhniIRwQ","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"Valores jerarquizados → Permite orden (ej. nivel estudios, interés en dejar de fumar)","guid":"ETYUOFzSwnq-g7DHnOn9kA","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"38","text":"Ejemplos → Dolor (leve/moderado/intenso), hábito tabáquico (nunca fumador/exfumador/activo)","guid":"ybwrjQFm7z0M5si2liIh6w","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"32","text":"Variables\\NCuantitativas","guid":"Z8TGxWW9mbABfQhuJb8X-g","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"Valores numéricos reales","guid":"oKCnPSm6pdsx2JDB39ft3A","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"Tipos:","guid":"0ZunzQeGZSj5Cd0qZtKOCg","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"Discretas → Valores enteros aislados (ej. número hijos, intentos dejar de fumar)","guid":"aShvLaAf03ld9uHwbDpz6Q","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"43","text":"Continuas → Valores infinitos entre dos números enteros, permiten decimales (ej. peso, talla, edad)","guid":"2ac7Pjj8rCwWzzr3S21hYg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"26","text":"Escalas de\\NMedición","guid":"qEfC4HMvezccujIs8ML1cA","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"Nominal → Etiquetas para distinguir sin jerarquía (ej. sexo, estado civil)","guid":"9iQIXTiJEG9UoxaGuqftrw","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"Ordinal → Orden implícito en valores (ej. gravedad de enfermedad)","guid":"nkyea9CiGxAJYVHLcjLXNw","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"Intervalo → Unidades numéricas con distancia clara entre valores (ej. temperatura)","guid":"ndxQKV_SQX4xZxLIF5JkkA","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"46","text":"Razón → Igual que intervalo, pero 0 indica ausencia (ej. peso)","guid":"X6XCRTtS5bWp2AHA8jC8MA","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"26","text":"Relación entre\\NEscalas","guid":"qaUO1bfmQRdZ6zIbewAfDQ","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"Posible convertir intervalo/razón a ordinal","guid":"zEXUZJ1wnbjN_31dCINGEg","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"51","text":"No es posible pasar de escala de menor precisión a mayor","guid":"ti21C-ykMcE2S23AcwSu4A","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"26","text":"Codificación de datos\\Nen bioestadística","guid":"-MQ9E9tRo-iRfNRHXNwZOA","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"• Codificación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"• Proceso de asignar códigos numéricos a etiquetas de categorías.","guid":"9zZPl6FBvNGAkDHm-3Leuw","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"• Ej.: Sexo → 1 = Varón, 2 = Mujer.","guid":"0MiBnbyapE5aDzkzMAffOg","children":[]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"54","text":"• Bases de datos\\N(BD)","guid":"3OIMH2t3U_kTdotJHTd0Bg","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"• Fichero estructurado con filas (individuos) y columnas (variables).","guid":"iMWFlMXLdBGMyiE7gZ_87A","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"• Formato:","guid":"uHOO1sQ7SL5IY527BcdecA","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"• Ancho → Cada individuo ocupa 1 fila; múltiples columnas representan variables.","guid":"k0vDB18bidfFX4jWlZ1tRw","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"• Largo → Cada individuo ocupa varias filas; útil para medidas repetidas.","guid":"k9u08-dkAaLCN491MmDiZA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"63","parent":"54","text":"• Ejemplo de variables","guid":"6hFek7zgsq_UX0Sjefq1cw","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"1. id → Identificación.","guid":"eoZo1QTYWN9PUqsQxn6XfA","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"63","text":"2. Sexo → 1 = Varón, 2 = Mujer.","guid":"xjUPAColMXRybMqK2VvNYg","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"63","text":"3. Edad → Años.","guid":"2S1XLQVnAWsrszMKkSJrLA","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"63","text":"4. Inicio tabaquismo → Edad inicio.","guid":"KuJTnxW0QUHfPGnAEQwZIg","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"63","text":"5. Numcig → Cigarrillos/día.","guid":"Bp9kZoD5uebqs4AA06GTWg","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"63","text":"6. Peso → kg.","guid":"TlTEQQMf6p7rYkPOr33u3Q","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"63","text":"7. Talla → cm.","guid":"vYdRYazcufAK0yFMs_BmPA","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"63","text":"8. Grupo → 1 = Intervención, 2 = Control.","guid":"tOZRxhXBREe8iLc8T8EszA","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"63","text":"9. Estado civil → 1 = Soltero, 2 = Casado, 3 = Viudo, 4 = Divorciado, 5 = Otros.","guid":"VrHoc3sJRWQctPMFKTfuNQ","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"63","text":"10-12. Fecha inclusión\\N→ Día, mes, año.","guid":"v-irImA8KnXamP8qL3fFzw","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"10. Estudios → Nivel educativo (codificado).","guid":"wYY1GgEGOEYGirQhNYDprA","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"11. Interés en dejar de fumar → 0-3 (codificado).","guid":"raQxLj3OolGL87uYf5_3eQ","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"73","text":"12. Abandono tabaco → 1 = Sí, 2 = No.","guid":"3L0CjK_bIYX5ZErO3HV75w","children":[]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"63","text":"15-17. Fecha final seguimiento → Día, mes, año.","guid":"ob9qnEEY-CqCr7Ir5StN1Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"26","text":"Clasificación:","guid":"Zo4lKxjJRUDaCLWiwfCdmw","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"Simples → Acceso directo a su dimensión (peso, estatura)","guid":"P6km-AK32FNba_uzPObQHA","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"78","text":"Complejas → Integran múltiples variables (estado nutricional)","guid":"NchMnT-NxCenWHDPyak3cw","children":[]}]},{"id":"81","parent":"26","text":"Clasificación\\NEpidemiológica:","guid":"Kui1ZCaILbJehu-QAKwhzw","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"Dependiente → Variable de efecto/respuesta","guid":"itRrUgoemnpROBmIz-p4KA","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"81","text":"Independiente → Variable causa posible de la dependiente","guid":"ECCaOgQ4CB0Om2OXpEfzmw","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"26","text":"Calidad de la\\NInformación Estadística","guid":"a37Ve42xUKtZGmx1qPQNoA","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"Validez: Medida refleja el estado verdadero (ej. fiebre no es un indicador suficiente de tifoidea)","guid":"pX_4FRCm4qeZptOwqr4e2g","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"Error: Diferencia entre\\Nmedida y valor real","guid":"Izu69SORedonIy9HVEY8Cw","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"Errores Sistemáticos → Desviación constante (ej. falta de definiciones claras, mala calibración)","guid":"qtkc_fi6VTLYmbdURwFypQ","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"Errores Aleatorios → Variación no identificada, afecta más a escalas continuas","guid":"WFi4xyS7czVjD3zaEnXmpg","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"84","text":"Fuentes\\Nde Error","guid":"mGplI-WSMhHyQ46lkFJZuw","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"Planificación Deficiente → Errores por falta de definiciones claras, heterogeneidad en observación","guid":"catlHs4cYUYt7EHGAIZQiw","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"89","text":"Observador → Variabilidad en destrezas, entrenamiento necesario","guid":"gz4M_8AMexVoFhNHGpdJ1Q","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"89","text":"Unidad de Observación → Variación propia del sujeto (ej. cambios de diagnóstico)","guid":"Tf_wZ_tzgT_6_sBF3Q15Mg","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"89","text":"Instrumento → Defectos de calibración, falta de fiabilidad","guid":"R_pn8RvbEmFzWXhXj7D8Sw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"26","text":"Tablas\\NEstadísticas","guid":"DvLWMvPJT-zFhfQLg9VU-g","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"Etapas en Construcción\\Nde una Tabla","guid":"EEpzezASl0MpEDIdTcJ7QA","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"Definir propósito","guid":"ygR0Mkid-XFo6jc7R2l4LA","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"95","text":"Título → Indica qué, cómo, dónde y cuándo se recolectaron los datos","guid":"Pn7tRthlbQ4jpBjxOGwADg","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"95","text":"Asignar variables a filas/columnas","guid":"9cVOakN_9fJbiTAEmhqwbA","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"95","text":"Colocar frecuencias y porcentajes","guid":"hMrVsQwQ4XNVfN0Mb28cZg","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"95","text":"Agregar notas explicativas y fuente de información","guid":"-iANQqklc27KLRBPXIDKPQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"94","text":"Tipos de Tablas","guid":"fiS5P3dmEClL_5D_ieoYXQ","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"Distribución de Frecuencias → Clasifica según un solo criterio","guid":"RMVlCo8M8VcW31EVioW5lA","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"101","text":"Tablas de Asociación → Relacionan dos o más variables","guid":"mAp8Hic3mT_oaDQqwjYQvQ","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"101","text":"Casos Especiales → Cuando una unidad tiene múltiples atributos, es